{"tid":1132320,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（估歌手）IT男為追求音樂夢放棄過百萬年薪","createTime":"2019-04-30T08:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T09:44:18.000Z","uid":122522,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"12ec1e44b262f96f444b7340df6feb86602bdd68","tid":1132320,"uid":122522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:22:08.000Z","msg":"老實講佢唱功算係新人算係中上（雖然都唔算新），點解香港冇咩人留意，聽佢個訪問自信爆棚，睇得出佢好想導正香港樂壇同藝術，香港再多kpop系、娘炮真係冇人再聽廣東歌！肯放棄高薪玩音樂呢個決定已經夠pop!<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2682111/org/361b247c6d10b7dcad997329b4e27cfe.jpg/4Qpc79BjOTmCU0hZBtaKAYI5q870BF9Ze1g0tHtYNLQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2682111%2Forg%2F361b247c6d10b7dcad997329b4e27cfe.jpg%2F4Qpc79BjOTmCU0hZBtaKAYI5q870BF9Ze1g0tHtYNLQ&h=25c68ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2682109/org/68092aff7b70af12c2b9a810ec65104f.jpg/nZEtHA-gr1MGc1nkJmhLktCnuvmmjk-4_yKXlP8il5Q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2682109%2Forg%2F68092aff7b70af12c2b9a810ec65104f.jpg%2FnZEtHA-gr1MGc1nkJmhLktCnuvmmjk-4_yKXlP8il5Q&h=4855c7aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2682100/org/b595c8ac730102071cc39ea10be4cbbd.jpg/bpu-nW9_IClwBAsz-QmPClScegBozkU7ckH5qHJB-ag\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2682100%2Forg%2Fb595c8ac730102071cc39ea10be4cbbd.jpg%2Fbpu-nW9_IClwBAsz-QmPClScegBozkU7ckH5qHJB-ag&h=131c2f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7HpyGpL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7HpyGpL.jpg&h=2ff9fd46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/30/160424_90037c2c5abe240614503615acaf35fb.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F30%2F160424_90037c2c5abe240614503615acaf35fb.jpeg&h=bca94506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/30/160520_6bb76ba8fbff3a8b798f2130f5abd598.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F30%2F160520_6bb76ba8fbff3a8b798f2130f5abd598.jpeg&h=e5b44776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾獲陳奕迅加持 藍調歌手易容Busking：觀眾對素人係寬容啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/演唱現場/318334/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%2F318334%2F&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1anpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=e5f300f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/演唱現場/318334/</a><br />\n<br />\n其實符致逸由2001年已開始擔任作曲工作，後來更為了<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">追求音樂夢而放棄了高薪厚職的科技工作</span></span>。<span style=\"color: red;\">曾為陳奕迅《一切還好》、《我們都寂寞》、《路&hellip;一直都在》、鄭秀文《我就是愛你不害怕》等大熱作品作曲</span>，亦獲提名台灣《第26屆金曲獎》的「最佳新人獎」。<br />\n在香港出道不知不覺已來到第五個年頭，卻是<span style=\"color: red;\">紅歌不紅人</span>，大家在麥記買早餐時大概也會聽過「Flying By~是我的寂寞神態~」又或是近期「若是自己也會心死   ~實在值得我被放棄~」，《靈魂獨舞》及新歌《值得放棄》兩首作品自然是琅琅上口，但大家又會否願意多花時間留意這位有心有才華的音樂人？"},{"pid":"c31051814046be05121ff9926b9a223bdebb8233","tid":1132320,"uid":122134,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fanfest.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/korath.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffanfest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fkorath.gif&h=80fdb007&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec863e4d83152d688a2c47bb0fa705ae985b6c68","tid":1132320,"uid":188310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c31051814046be05121ff9926b9a223bdebb8233","tid":1132320,"uid":122134,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fanfest.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/korath.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffanfest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fkorath.gif&h=80fdb007&s=